Create invoice class
  - should have:
    - remote ID
    - text
    - status flag: unpaid | paid | written-off
    - remote invoice created?
    - due date
  
Add to agreement:
  - flag indicating if unpaid invoices exist?

daily rake task:
  sync clients
  create local invoices
  create remote invoices for all local invoices without remote invoices
  sync paid status of invoices
  update unpaid agreements
  
Reporting:
